text: Nicolae Spîrcu (born 6 December 1969) is a Romanian rower. He competed at the 1992 Summer Olympics and the 1996 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1969 births Category:Living people Category:Romanian male rowers Category:Olympic rowers of Romania Category:Rowers at the 1992 Summer Olympics Category:Rowers at the 1996 Summer Olympics Category:People from Olt County
